@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rimzfd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v1 + (wp.sin(v1 + 0.95) / 0.92))
    tmp = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.70 + v0 + 0.00) - tmp))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.08 / v2 + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
